職位要求:

至少三至五年以上製作公司創作經驗; 獨立統籌，創作影片包括前中後期製作；篩選項目; 熟悉製作流程，有豐富影視製作，凝聚團隊，有應變能力處理突發危機，協作劇本和拍攝要求策劃拍攝.

To apply, please send us your resume / CV to us. Personal data collected will be used for recruitment purposes only.

Job Duties:

1. Conduct business risk and internal control review for major operating processes of the Headquarters and Business Units; complete audit working papers and draft audit reports;

2. Follow up rectification status of the identified audit matters;

3. Assist in compiling internal control-related policies and procedures;

4. Assist in compiling ESG report;

5. Handle the other tasks as assigned by the department head.

工作職責:

1. 就總部層面主要運作流程及集團下屬經營單位，進行經營風險及內部控制檢視工作，完成審計底稿並編寫審計報告（中文或英文）；

2. 定期跟進審計問題的整改情況；

3. 協助編寫相關內控管理制度及流程；

4. 協助編寫集團之環境、社會及管治報告；

5. 完成交辦的其他工作。



Job Duties:

1. Possesses 3 years or above external or internal audit experiences;

2. Possesses the Certified Internal Auditors (CIA) qualification;

3. Knowledge in HK listing rules and working experience in Chinese companies is preferred;

4. Strong analytical and communication skills; complete tasks independently;

5. Team work, responsible, proactive and attentive;

6. Good reporting writing skills and fluent Mandarin;

7. Occasional travel on a job-by-job basis.

8. Candidate with less experience will be considered as Internal Audit Assistant

工作要求:

1. 具有3年或以上在會計師事務所從事外部審計或在企業從事內部審計工作之經驗；

2. 具有國際內部審計師資格(CIA)；

3. 對上市條例有一定瞭解, 及有中資企業工作經驗者優先；

4. 具有較強的分析能力和溝通協調能力，能獨立完成工作任務；

5. 具有良好的團隊合作精神、有責任感、積極主動及細心;

6. 具有良好的報告寫作能力及流利普通話；

7. 按工作需要出差內地。

For more details of our company, please visit our website at http://www.ifeng.com/

